_sText:
Recent CS:GO map by CaD ported by me

Info: This map try's to balance beginners / advanced skilled players.
Not the hardest thing but at full speed it takes some planning routing and allot of skill.
Yes the lights come from magic sources and make very little sense, should not be to much of a bother how ever.
Small "bonus" at the end of the level.

Their is a secret in the level good luck finding it.

Map made for your enjoyment i hope you do enjoy ;-).
